code: import axios from"axios";export var validateInviteLink=function validateInviteLink(hash){return axios.get('https://gateway.icdcoder.de/invite/validate/'+hash).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(e){console.log('error',e);});};export var submitInvite=function submitInvite(inviteData){return axios.post('https://gateway.icdcoder.de/invite/submit/',inviteData).then(function(response){if(response.data.tokenData.accessToken){localStorage.setItem("user",JSON.stringify(response.data.tokenData));localStorage.setItem("userType",response.data.userType);localStorage.setItem("loggedIn","true");}return response.data;}).catch(function(e){console.log('error',e);});};
